title: Barney McAll and Greg Lloyd: the ex-pat piano club heads home
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Barney McAll and Greg Lloyd: the ex-p... Barney McAll and Greg Lloyd: the ex-pat piano club heads home 1 hr ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
From playing with charades with Beyonce and Jay Z to performing with traditional Algerian musicians is admittedly a stretch, but Barney McAll and Greg Lloyd headed overseas with the same idea: to expand their horizons. McAll went to New York and Lloyd to Paris, neither jazz pianist knowing what would happen next. Start the conversation, or Read more at Sydney Morning Herald.
